    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  COVID-19 infection and fatality rates vary considerably between countries. We present preliminary evidence that these variations may in part reflect ethnic differences in the frequencies of polymorphic alleles of\n                  <jats:italic>SERPINA1</jats:italic>\n                  , coding for alpha-1 antitrypsin, the major blood serine protease inhibitor.\n                </jats:p>",
